The short version (not a substitute for the terms below)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
If you are a clinician, supervisor, educator, researcher, student,
learner, parent, caregiver, self-advocate, school, clinic, or non-profit
using this Software to make people's lives better - go ahead. Use it.
Fork it. Improve it. Share your improvements. That is exactly why it
exists.
If you are trying to turn this code into a paid product, a paid service,
or any other offering whose primary value proposition to a customer is
this Software or its output - stop. You do not have permission. Contact
the Licensor for a commercial license.
Being paid for your own clinical, educational, or supervisory work while
using this Software with the people you serve is fine. Selling the
Software itself, or access to it, or a product built on it, is not.
